<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6994670>
    dc:description "Figure 23. Australonaucoris congrex male: dorsal habitus (a), genital capsule with parameres and terga IX and X removed (b), left paramere (c), right paramere (d). Sizes are not proportional among figures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6994670/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6994668>
    dc:description "Figure 22. Afronaucoris obscuratus male: dorsal habitus (a), genital capsule with terga IX and X removed (b), left and right parameres (c), distal part of aedeagus (d). Sizes are not proportional among figures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6994668/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6994674>
    dc:description "Figure 24. Indonaucoris minutus gen. nov., sp. nov.: dorsal habitus (a), ventral habitus (b), genital capsule (c), genital capsule with terga IX and X removed (d), left and right parameres (e), dorsal and ventral views of mesothoracic leg (f), dorsal and ventral views of metathoracic leg (g). Sizes are not proportional among figures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6994674/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

